Package: pitchR
Type: Package
Title: Statcast Data and Salaries for MLB Pitchers
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Josh Yamamoto <yamamojo@reed.edu>, Andy Zhao <andjzhao@reed.edu>, Joshua Park <jopark@reed.edu>
Maintainer: Josh Yamamoto <yamamojo@reed.edu>
Description: Statcast data from baseball savant was joined with salary data scraped from sporttrac in order to provide a comprehensive source of both advanced analytics as well as salaries for MLB starting pitchers.
